                <span class="block pl-4 text-content-muted">= (3/6 × base(3)) × 1.1</span>
                <span class="block pl-4 text-content-muted">= 1.5 × 3 × 1.1</span>
                <span class="block pl-4 text-accent">= 4.95 orders/day</span>
                <span class="block text-content-muted mt-1">Source: MARKET_RESEARCH · Confidence: MEDIUM</span>
